com.sun.mirror.type

Interface ArrayType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ReferenceType, TypeMirror
    Deprecated. 
    All components of this API have been superseded by the standardized annotation processing API. The replacement for the functionality of this interface is ArrayType.

    @Deprecated
public interface ArrayType
extends ReferenceType
    Represents an array type. A multidimensional array type is represented as an array type whose component type is also an array type.
    Since:
    1.5
